article.description: — DeAndre Dishman had 16 points as Middle Tennessee got past Winthrop 76-65 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Dishman leads Middle Tennessee over Winthrop 76-65
article.linkText: Dishman leads Middle Tennessee over Winthrop 76-65
article.story: MURFREESBORO, Tenn. -- — DeAndre Dishman had 16 points as Middle Tennessee got past Winthrop 76-65 on Tuesday night. Donovan Sims had 16 points for Middle Tennessee (3-0). Josh Corbin had 14 points for the Eagles (2-1). D.J. Burns Jr. added 14 points. Cory Hightower had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25------ Information from: Automated Insights, http://automatedinsights.com/ ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
